<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.7.10">
<l>maṟaivalār kuṟaivilā ruṟaiyumūr vallavā ḻaṭikaḷ tammai</l>
<l>ciṟaikulā vaṇṭaṟai cōlaicūḻ kōlanī ḷāli nāṭaṉ</l>
<l>kaṟaiyulā vēlvalla kaliyaṉvā yoliyivai kaṟṟu vallār</l>
<l>iṟaivarā yirunilaṅ kāvalpūṇ ṭiṉpanaṉ keytu vārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who are skilled, learning these poems by Kaliyaṉ,</l>
<l rend="indent">skilled with a blood-spattered spear,</l>
<l>Countryman of beautiful, vast Āli surrounded by groves</l>
<l rend="indent">where swarms of winged bees hum,</l>
<l>About the god of Vallavāḻ, the city where dwell infallible Vedic experts,</l>
<l>Undertaking the protection of this vast land as lords,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will fully attain happiness.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
